messages.templateId: Well, damn. Well, why the hell are you courting this Skier so? Buffs you with cash? Promised you a share? But to hell with him, and you too. Get out of here, don't want to see your mug right now.
Hm... well, alright. Old offenses are forgotten, let’s keep working. Just be careful around that Skier character, he’s a shady dude.
Is the job done? Good, then here is your reward.
I have nothing to say. It scares me to think of who and why might need this chemical.

Good shit, gonna continue working together. Here's your reward. I've remembered you, so drop by sometimes. Various jobs always come up, all of different nature, but people expire fast these days, if you know what I mean.

You’re a damn Pinkerton! Helped me out big time! So, you found my idiot errand boy? Well, screw him. If you do something similar, you'll get smoked like him too. Go on, buzz off, I've got some stuff to do.
Ah-hah, now that was a stirrup if I ever seen one! I got word from all channels that some devil is at large and grounded quite a bunch of people. You rock, get your reward.
And he said nothing was there! Although they might be empty. Need to check. In any case, here's your cut.
When the deed is done, go get your fun. Let's see what will come of it.

How long I live and wonder still. How was he surviving all this time? He can’t put two words together! Whatever. Let's first disinfect all this and wash it with cologne, and then open it and have a look.
Proper work, Rambo, grab your prize. By the way, you dropped some really important brass there. They shit their pants good.
It seems this problem is not solved, but only got more complicated. Well, whatever. Come what may.
Now we’re talking! Rouble’s dropping, and green ones grow like buns of a roadside hooker, ha-ha. Wait for a call from Peacekeeper, you freaking careerist.
Well, great. Now it’s time to get as far as possible while they do their experiments. We can have a look later.
All this tech shit is clearly not for me, the picture is hazed and the signal is shit, but I’ve already spotted some “fat rats” while you were setting the last cams up. Thanks, huge help!
Finally dragged it all. Awesome! I won’t disappoint you either. So, seen any USECs around the cars? Well, doesn't matter.
Good shit, you fucked those morons up properly. Alright, mate, see ya.
Fuck's sake, it's all encrypted. Need to call the four-eyes again. Alright, you've done your part of the deal as agreed. I'll figure something out what to do with this crap.
Now that is right on! Well, now we’re tied up good, bro. Awesome that you didn’t chicken out at the last moment. Now I can fill you in on some real serious business.
Oh, so you actually brought some? Splendid! Hands still intact after touching all these chems? I’ll get the eggheads working then, let them tinker with the stuff.

Opa, here's my goodie! So, it indeed was in the USEC cottages, you're saying? And the damn chopper was there too? Looks like the rumors were true. I knew it couldn't have gone far. Otherwise, there would've been a big uproar! The USECs had no reason to spread the info through, they were probably waiting for orders from the command, but, well, you know what happened. Alrighty, here's your reward.
Scavs eased up a bit, hope they won’t get too greedy and ask for more, but that’s my pain, not yours. Nicely done!
There you go. Now I'm certain you won't piss your pants if some shit hits the fan.
Looks like everything's cool, my fellas are on the spot, and I think that it's gonna be the last surprise for those fuckers. Thanks for the help.
Welcome to the crew, homie. So, down to business?
Big thanks. Now we know where they are so we don't have to take any chances. Here's the reward for a job well done, brother.
So the only thing they want is to shoot each other. That’s just wrong. Well, kid, I know you at least tried.
So the only thing they want is to shoot each other. That’s just wrong. Well, kid, I know you at least tried.
My contacts received everything they needed. Good job, will be glad to work with you more, mercenary.
